<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA516_05_IH_0007</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema516_05.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema516_05_ih_0007 paging">
      <section class="title type2 score">
        <h2 data-head="7" class="is_star2" lang="y">둘레가 48 ㎝이고 가로가 18 ㎝인 직사각형의 넓이는 몇 ㎠인지 구하려고 합니다. 물음에 답해 보세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">직사각형의 세로는 몇 ㎝인지 구해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center">
            <div class="input_area">
              <span>&#40;</span>
              <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="6"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>&#41; ㎝</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 해설 -->
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p>
                    <span lang="y">직사각형의 세로를</span>
                    <span class="nemo"></span>
                    <span lang="y">㎝라고 하면 (18+</span>
                    <span class="nemo"></span>
                    <span lang="y">)×2=48, 18+</span>
                    <span class="nemo"></span>
                    <span lang="y">=24,</span>
                    <span class="nemo"></span>
                    <span lang="y">=6입니다.</span><br />
                    <span lang="y">따라서 직사각형의 세로는 6 ㎝입니다.</span>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">직사각형의 넓이는 몇 ㎠ 인지 구해 보세요.</h3>
          <div class="question_box justify_center">
            <div class="input_area">
              <span>&#40;</span>
              <div class="input_wrap answer1">
                <math-field type="number" data-answer-single="108"></math-field>
              </div>
              <span>&#41; ㎠</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- 해설 -->
          <div class="solve_area">
            <div class="inner_solve">
              <div class="flex">
                <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
                <div class="conts_solve">
                  <p lang="y">(직사각형의 넓이)=18×6=108 (㎠)</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
